Package org.rapaio.jupyter.kernel.display.text

Class ANSI

java.lang.Object
org.rapaio.jupyter.kernel.display.text.ANSI
public final class ANSI extends Object
This incorporates some commands for manipulation of the text output format for Jupyter notebook output and error output.

Guidance follows:

  • PyPi ansi-text
  • Wikipedia on ANSI escape code
